snippet.title: Super Crane Bug
snippet.description:
A retro match 3 about a Bug with many tools! 
You have to juggle playing around each tool before the board fills up.

Be a bug, use a crane, do a match

Play now on itch.io 
http://calixjumio.itch.io/super-crane
